               <scopecontent id="aspace_2d98ff7e7bd46dcd770587a0cf3a662c">
                  <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
                  <p>In 1930, Haynes did a survey of the work of the YMCA in South Africa. In 1947 he conducted a similar study in other African nations. This work resulted in Haynes being chosen as consultant on Africa by the World Committee of YMCAs.</p>
